snippet.title: Creaturemin | Pikmin Direct 2024 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Creaturemin is an upcoming Pikmin 2 Mod that aims to change the game completely! Featuring all new mechanics, six pikmin types, enemies, and areas. New quality of life features like enhanced disbanding and organisation, as well as Master Ship storage.
For more information, check out the Hocotate Newsletter Discord!
h ttps://discord.gg/N7pQHuKH
